PRETORIA, South Africa, February 28, 2017/APO/ --
                                                
                        President Jacob Zuma will on Friday, 03 March 2017, officially open the National House of Traditional Leaders for its 2017/2018 business. The official opening is undertaken by the President annually after State of the Nation Address.  







Details of the event are as follows:

Date: Friday, 03 March 2017 

Time: 0h00

Venue: Old Assembly Chamber, Parliament, Cape Town





Enquiries: Dr Bongani Ngqulunga on 082 308 9373 or bongani@presidency.gov.za.